     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet RevisionIndikationDHR</b></p><a name=\"RevisionIndikationDHR\"> </a><a name=\"hcRevisionIndikationDHR\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/RevisionIndication</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-femur_acetabulum_osteolysis\">femur_acetabulum_osteolysis</a></td><td>Aseptisk løsning af femur- og acetabulumkomp. med osteolyse</td><td>Femur og acetabulum med osteolyse</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-femur_acetabulum\">femur_acetabulum</a></td><td>Aseptisk løsning af femur- og acetabulumkomp. uden osteolyse</td><td>Femur og acetabulum</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-femur_osteolysis\">femur_osteolysis</a></td><td>Aseptisk løsning alene af femurkomp. med osteolyse</td><td>Femur med osteolyse</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-femur\">femur</a></td><td>Aseptisk løsning alene af femurkomp. uden osteolyse</td><td>Femur</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-acetabulum_osteolysis\">acetabulum_osteolysis</a></td><td>Aseptisk løsning alene af acetabulumkomp. med osteolyse</td><td>Acetabulum med osteolyse</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionIndication.html#RevisionIndication-acetabulum\">acetabulum</a></td><td>Aseptisk løsning alene af acetabulumkomp. uden osteolyse</td><td>Acetabulum